OL,6,FA mother has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fkilling her three-month-old daughter.
OL,9,FKaylani Kalanzi was on the radar of
OL,10,Fsocial services even before she was
OL,11,Fborn and placed on a child protection
OL,12,Fplan, the Old Bailey was told.
OL,14,FOn July 8 2024, she was admitted to
OL,15,Fhospital having been violently shaken,
OL,16,Fwith an impact to her head.
OL,18,FShe suffered catastrophic brain
OL,19,Finjuries as well as a broken leg and
OL,20,Fribs, and died in hospital 15 days
OL,21,Flater.
