OL,6,FProsecutor Zoe Johnson KC had told
OL,7,Fjurors that Kaylani's parents were
OL,8,F"selfish and irresponsible", putting
OL,9,Ftheir abusive relationship above their
OL,10,Fchild's needs.
OL,12,FShe said that mother Nazli Merthoca
OL,13,Fwas responsible for causing Kaylani's
OL,14,Fdeath, and her partner Herbert Kalanzi
OL,15,Ffailed in his duty to protect his
OL,16,Fchild.
OL,18,FBoth Merthoca, 24, and Mr Kalanzi, 35,
OL,19,Ffrom East Ham, east London, denied
OL,20,Fwrongdoing and declined to give
OL,21,Fevidence at their Old Bailey trial.
