OL,6,FOn Tuesday a jury cleared Merthoca of
OL,7,Fmurder but found her guilty of the
OL,8,Flesser alternative charge of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter, after deliberating for
OL,10,Fmore than 15 hours.
OL,12,FMr Kalanzi was cleared by the jury of
OL,13,Fcausing or allowing Kaylani's death.
OL,15,FHe was formally acquitted of her
OL,16,Fmurder on the directions of Judge Mark
OL,17,FLucraft KC.
OL,19,FMerthoca wiped away tears in the dock
OL,20,Fas she was remanded into custody to be
OL,21,Fsentenced on December 15.
